Name: Physical Trough Solar Field

Caption.String: Usage tip:  To configure the loop, choose whether to edit SCAs, HCEs or defocus order.  Select assemblies by clicking one or dragging the mouse over multiple items. Assign types to selected items by pressing keys 1-4.
The specification below is only for one loop in the solar field.

Items.StringList: Solar Salt|Caloria|Hitec XL|VP-1|Hitec|Dowtherm Q|Dowtherm RP|Therminol 59|Therminol 66|Pressurized Water|User-defined...

L_rnr_pb.Label: Length of runner pipe in pb

L_rnr_per_xpan.Label: Threshold length of straight runner pipe without an expansion loop

L_xpan_hdr.Label: Combined perpendicular lengths of each header expansion loop

L_xpan_rnr.Label: Combined perpendicular lengths of each runner expansion loop

Min_rnr_xpans.Label: Minimum number of expansion loops per single-diameter runner section

N_hdr_per_xpan.Label: Number of collector loops per expansion loop

SolarAz.Label: Initial condition for solar azimuth angle

accept_init.Label: In acceptance testing mode - require steady-state startup

accept_loc.Label: In acceptance testing mode - temperature sensor location (1=hx,2=loop)

calc_design_pipe_vals.Label: Calculate temps and pressures at design conditions for runners and headers

combo_htf_type.Label: Field HTF fluid

custom_sf_pipe_sizes.Label: Use custom solar field pipe diams, wallthks, and lengths

field_htf_cp_avg.Label: field htf spec heat at avg T

min_inner_diameter.Label: Minimum absorber inner diameter in loop
